{"tid":1974754,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員同我入嚟！！！","createTime":"2020-04-16T05:20:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T07:57:56.000Z","uid":340040,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a35c86c16400058e32c2aa8cb0e3d589cd387c","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"9月就立法會選舉,先唔理成效、港共會唔會DQ民選議員<br />\n大家都知道壞咗係個制度，呢到就唔多講，肯定既係對家會喺投票日搞好多小動作<br />\n但係選舉依然會進行，破局、攬炒仍然係我哋嘅目標<br />\n上年區議會選舉某啲票站有大量問題選票或者程序有問題，某啲票站主任做嘢嘅方法都令人質疑投票嘅結果<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">公務員一定要報名做票站職員，入去票站mon住佢</span></span>，高grade既更加要做，因為票站主任有話事權<br />\n<br />\n無論最終過唔過半，都要有自己人mon住個過程，先至有彈藥架嗎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路</span>"},{"pid":"adbc5cce08b9ad32ff8160034b149a044b3e0657","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f50be3bd002d55d65b9a1b4c63035204cb6d6bc","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8e31be0220df4f20e7db81012f5383ad945fbbd3","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:21:21.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"1cb2d30d4bc63b40cdbc093c587c2d6fb2fb2d62","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fb3e4e5cdf6ee9d2823447969ad6c6ff9e036c","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3641d2a977942a953cd4eaa32ff25ae0972b2c1b","tid":1974754,"uid":340040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T05:21:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a08f9f7a65bf1ab98a3f03030157ba41f3a87a58","tid":1974754,"u